                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "| Feature | IntraVox | SharePoint | Confluence |\n|---------|----------|------------|------------|\n| Open Source | Yes | No | No |\n| Self-hosted | Yes | Optional | Optional |\n| License costs | Free | Expensive | Expensive |\n| GDPR Compliant | Full | Complex | Complex |\n| Nextcloud Integration | Native | No | No |"
